TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Prisoner's Dilemma and Dynamical Systems Associated to Non-Cooperative Games
AU  - Smale, Steve
AB  - [A new way of looking at repeated games is introduced which incorporates a bounded memory and rationality. In these terms, a resolution of the prisoner's dilemma is given.]
